1
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:08,159
I didn't expect

2
00:01:08,840 --> 00:01:10,599
you'd come to such a boring place with me.

3
00:01:11,719 --> 00:01:13,079
I'm just curious.

4
00:01:15,599 --> 00:01:16,680
I told the organizer

5
00:01:17,319 --> 00:01:18,359
you're my girlfriend.

6
00:01:18,959 --> 00:01:20,319
Don't say anything wrong later.

7
00:01:24,719 --> 00:01:25,200
Okay.

8
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:33,120
Cheers.

9
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:33,719
Cheers.

10
00:01:33,719 --> 00:01:34,200
Here.

11
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:38,680
This is

12
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:40,280
Luminous Turban Snail.

13
00:01:42,760 --> 00:01:43,319
So beautiful.

14
00:01:44,599 --> 00:01:45,799
They are endangered species.

15
00:01:47,239 --> 00:01:49,239
They should live and reproduce in the sea,

16
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,480
not be placed here

17
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:51,760
for the enjoyment of the upper class

18
00:01:52,319 --> 00:01:53,280
and collected by the wealthy.

19
00:01:54,879 --> 00:01:56,400
But they can be auctioned off

20
00:01:56,719 --> 00:01:57,959
for a large sum of money

21
00:01:58,159 --> 00:01:59,519
to donate to poor children,

22
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:01,239
which is also a contribution to the human society.

23
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:05,480
Humans are always so arrogant,

24
00:02:05,879 --> 00:02:07,120
thinking themselves as the dominators.

25
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:09,520
And who knows

26
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:10,240
where the money will end up?

27
00:02:12,039 --> 00:02:12,759
Alright, Moon.

28
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:14,840
Let's not talk about this.

29
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,120
What do you want to eat?

30
00:02:16,439 --> 00:02:16,960
I'll get it for you.

31
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:26,000
Moon.

32
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:28,280
Bro.

33
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,039
It's okay.

34
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:31,199
Just sit here.

35
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:32,800
Okay.

36
00:02:33,599 --> 00:02:35,919
Now, let's welcome the organizer of this ball

37
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,439
to give a speech.

38
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:42,680
Everyone,

39
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,199
today,

40
00:02:44,599 --> 00:02:46,400
we gather here because of the gifts from the sea

41
00:02:46,759 --> 00:02:49,400
and the mission of benevolence.

42
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:50,919
We are gathered here.

43
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,800
The shell carvings and pearls

44
00:02:53,919 --> 00:02:55,479
on display today

45
00:02:55,719 --> 00:02:59,000
are not only the crystallization of nature's art

46
00:02:59,879 --> 00:03:01,599
but also the carriers of love.

47
00:03:02,319 --> 00:03:03,639
They come from the deep sea

48
00:03:04,199 --> 00:03:06,960
and will become the beacon of hope

49
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:09,000
for those in need.

50
00:03:09,719 --> 00:03:10,159
Come on,

51
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:11,759
let's raise our glasses.

52
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:13,360
Moon,

53
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,520
for the light of hope.

54
00:03:15,199 --> 00:03:15,639
Cheers!

55
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,360
Cheers!

56
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:18,560
This isn't the place for trouble.

57
00:03:19,039 --> 00:03:19,439
Be good.

58
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:22,599
I'm not here to cause trouble.

59
00:03:23,039 --> 00:03:24,360
I just want to talk to him.

60
00:03:24,639 --> 00:03:25,280
If you have something to say,

61
00:03:25,719 --> 00:03:26,599
I'll pass it on for you.

62
00:03:28,159 --> 00:03:28,639
What?

63
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:30,719
You don't even believe me?

64
00:03:32,599 --> 00:03:33,840
I just want to tell him

65
00:03:34,479 --> 00:03:35,759
not to be so hypocritical.

66
00:03:37,319 --> 00:03:37,800
Fine.

67
00:03:38,199 --> 00:03:39,039
I'll go to the back hall

68
00:03:39,439 --> 00:03:40,280
to meet a friend.

69
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:04,599
Someone is watching you.

70
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:43,240
Why are you here?

71
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:47,319
I guess Qin Yeren will come.

72
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:50,199
I want to ask him how much he was involved in the past.

73
00:05:51,519 --> 00:05:52,439
Leave it to me.

74
00:05:53,199 --> 00:05:54,319
Don't make decisions like this.

75
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:57,480
My brother is in a business deal.

76
00:05:58,439 --> 00:06:00,000
He seems to buy Black Rock Island.

77
00:06:01,439 --> 00:06:02,519
He's dreaming.

78
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:05,560
Xie Group's financial strength

79
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:07,399
is not just about logistics.

80
00:06:08,439 --> 00:06:09,600
Once the project is signed,

81
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:12,000
you and your people will be driven away.

82
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:14,399
Are you concerned about me?

83
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:18,319
I'm just

84
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:20,959
protecting animals.

85
00:06:21,639 --> 00:06:22,399
Where is she?

86
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:23,680
Search over there.

87
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:24,920
Okay.

88
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:26,680
They're still here,

89
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:27,839
hiding under me.

90
00:06:32,879 --> 00:06:35,399
Your skin is not bulletproof.

91
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:37,519
Their target is you.

92
00:06:38,879 --> 00:06:40,839
It seems that it's not easy to be the Wolf King's woman.

93
00:06:41,199 --> 00:06:42,279
You're not only being rewarded,

94
00:06:42,959 --> 00:06:43,959
but also being assassinated.

95
00:06:52,279 --> 00:06:52,720
They're gone.

96
00:07:00,639 --> 00:07:01,639
Aren't you going to catch them?

97
00:07:02,399 --> 00:07:03,399
Just let them go?

98
00:07:04,439 --> 00:07:06,040
I'm not sure if they have any help.

99
00:07:06,959 --> 00:07:07,560
Now,

100
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:09,720
your safety is more important.

101
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:13,279
The man who investigated Xie Chen for me said

102
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:15,399
his most important goal tonight

103
00:07:15,759 --> 00:07:16,839
is to find something.

104
00:07:17,839 --> 00:07:18,439
What?

105
00:07:19,639 --> 00:07:20,319
I don't know yet.

106
00:07:24,839 --> 00:07:25,959
I'm going to find my brother.

107
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,240
He can't find me.

108
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:28,160
No need.

109
00:07:31,519 --> 00:07:33,399
He has a more troublesome thing to deal with.

110
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:45,879
Excuse me,

111
00:07:46,319 --> 00:07:46,839
sir,

112
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:48,519
someone reported that you stole in the venue.

113
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:49,759
Please cooperate with our body search.

114
00:07:55,079 --> 00:07:56,160
Are you kidding?

115
00:07:56,879 --> 00:07:57,959
Do you know who I am?

116
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,759
We don't care who you are.

117
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:01,160
Please cooperate with our body search.

118
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:21,279
Sorry.

119
00:08:27,519 --> 00:08:28,079
Did you get it?

120
00:08:30,759 --> 00:08:31,839
Didn't you leave my brother?

121
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:32,879
Why are you back?

122
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:34,080
Nice to meet you again.

123
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:35,399
A Che,

124
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:36,960
you didn't tell me

125
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:38,519
it was because of her when you asked me for help.

126
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:40,039
This is not the place to talk.

127
00:08:41,279 --> 00:08:41,840
Let's talk at home.

128
00:08:43,399 --> 00:08:44,559
She's not my family.

129
00:08:45,799 --> 00:08:46,879
Goodbye.

130
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:51,879
Your brother seems to dislike me.

131
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:54,759
He's like this to everyone.

132
00:08:55,039 --> 00:08:55,600
Don't mind it.

133
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:58,480
But he just said we would never meet again.

134
00:08:59,159 --> 00:09:00,639
Is he going to run away from home?

135
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:03,360
I can catch him wherever he goes.

136
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:05,639
Let's figure out

137
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:07,519
what Xie Chen is trading first.

138
00:09:17,159 --> 00:09:17,720
You regret?

139
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:22,039
Didn't you say you wanted to protect animals?

140
00:09:22,759 --> 00:09:24,399
Now you choose to stand on the side of the hunters.

141
00:09:27,279 --> 00:09:28,440
I will persuade him to stop.

142
00:09:29,519 --> 00:09:30,960
Can you promise me one thing?

143
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:37,080
As long as he is not doing something outrageous,

144
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:39,879
can you not hurt my brother?

145
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:42,600
What if

146
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,799
he does something evil?

147
00:09:46,399 --> 00:09:47,200
I know him.

148
00:09:47,639 --> 00:09:49,080
He's a kind person.

149
00:09:52,919 --> 00:09:53,759
I hope so.

150
00:09:58,799 --> 00:09:59,279
Here.

151
00:10:06,919 --> 00:10:08,039
It's my brother's car.

152
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:10,120
Let's see what your brother

153
00:10:10,279 --> 00:10:11,080
and Qin Yeren are doing.

154
00:10:21,519 --> 00:10:22,279
1123.

155
00:10:22,799 --> 00:10:23,519
My brother's birthday.

156
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:30,679
Anything else?

157
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:34,679
Why don't you let me try?

158
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,080
My birthday.

159
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:04,759
Brother.

160
00:11:05,799 --> 00:11:06,360
So,

161
00:11:06,399 --> 00:11:08,120
this is why you came to the banquet with me,

162
00:11:08,559 --> 00:11:09,080
right?

163
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:11,360
You said

164
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:14,080
you would come back after terminating the contract with Qin Yeren.

165
00:11:15,039 --> 00:11:16,720
But I saw the drawings on your desk.

166
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:27,080
This is for you.

167
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:28,360
Open it.

168
00:11:34,639 --> 00:11:35,440
Birthday present.

169
00:11:40,120 --> 00:11:40,960
Don't you like it?

170
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,039
It's too expensive.

171
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:44,720
I don't want it.

172
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:50,000
Did you hear that?

173
00:11:50,639 --> 00:11:51,320
She doesn't want it.

174
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:54,919
I warn you,

175
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:57,600
don't set foot in our territory again.

176
00:12:00,039 --> 00:12:01,080
She's young

177
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:03,120
and can't tell a bully from a friend,

178
00:12:03,240 --> 00:12:04,639
so she's fooled by you.

179
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:07,159
When you end up on the streets,

180
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:08,440
homeless,

181
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:09,519
she'll understand

182
00:12:10,159 --> 00:12:11,720
who really loves her.

183
00:12:15,879 --> 00:12:17,279
The air is too polluted here.

184
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:19,240
Let's go.

185
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:42,159
If it's too heavy,

186
00:12:42,600 --> 00:12:43,720
I can walk by myself.

187
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:49,759
You're too light,

188
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:51,600
even lighter than before.

189
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:55,440
Looks like he didn't feed you enough.

190
00:12:58,159 --> 00:12:59,000
It's so hot.

191
00:12:59,919 --> 00:13:01,600
Why don't you put me down?

192
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:30,720
You haven't said much on the way.

193
00:13:31,279 --> 00:13:33,720
Are you worried about your land being taken over by developers?

194
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:36,919
Maybe I can talk to my brother

195
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:38,600
in the name of nature conservation

196
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:40,799
to give up the project of Black Rock Island.

197
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:42,759
You still want to go to him.

198
00:13:56,720 --> 00:13:57,720
I'll have someone

199
00:13:59,720 --> 00:14:00,840
deal with those troubles.

200
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:08,480
But you still look troubled.

201
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:10,960
Don't frown.

202
00:14:16,120 --> 00:14:16,840
You know what?

203
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:20,039
I just had a

204
00:14:20,679 --> 00:14:21,919
terrible idea.

205
00:14:23,240 --> 00:14:25,399
I want to catch all the men

206
00:14:26,120 --> 00:14:26,759
who get close to you,

207
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:27,799
throw them away,

208
00:14:28,600 --> 00:14:29,320
and tear them apart.

209
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:32,480
Are you protecting your master

210
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:34,080
or guarding your food?

211
00:14:34,759 --> 00:14:35,639
I'm jealous.

212
00:14:36,399 --> 00:14:37,120
Really.

213
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:38,720
Really what?

214
00:14:43,279 --> 00:14:43,960
Selfish,

215
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:45,960
stupid, ridiculous.

216
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:47,960
Straightforward.

217
00:14:50,879 --> 00:14:51,840
But I'm glad

218
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:58,120
you're happy

219
00:14:58,879 --> 00:14:59,519
seeing me go crazy.

220
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:02,559
It's not going crazy.

221
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:04,639
It's a common human emotion

222
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:07,039
in certain situations.

223
00:15:09,360 --> 00:15:10,159
What emotion?

224
00:15:12,360 --> 00:15:14,480
Because of the brand,

225
00:15:15,240 --> 00:15:16,879
you have a possessiveness

226
00:15:17,480 --> 00:15:18,159
towards me.

227
00:15:19,639 --> 00:15:20,759
That's why you feel uncomfortable.

228
00:15:21,320 --> 00:15:22,639
I've been feeling terrible

229
00:15:23,679 --> 00:15:24,759
I've been feeling terrible.

230
00:15:26,279 --> 00:15:26,919
Don't worry,

231
00:15:28,120 --> 00:15:29,240
the brand will disappear.

232
00:15:35,399 --> 00:15:36,720
Then you'll leave

233
00:15:38,919 --> 00:15:39,840
when it disappears.

234
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:45,720
You can think of it this way,

235
00:15:47,159 --> 00:15:48,840
before the brand disappears,

236
00:15:51,000 --> 00:15:52,240
I'll always be by your side.

237
00:16:19,480 --> 00:16:20,639
Qin Yaxin, what are you up to?

238
00:16:22,360 --> 00:16:23,279
What a disappointment.

239
00:16:23,679 --> 00:16:24,519
I failed to catch the big one,

240
00:16:24,720 --> 00:16:26,000
but I caught a small one instead.

241
00:16:26,279 --> 00:16:27,879
You dare to set a trap to frame my brother.

242
00:16:28,279 --> 00:16:29,240
Do you want to die?

243
00:16:29,399 --> 00:16:30,360
I warn you,

244
00:16:30,639 --> 00:16:32,440
be polite when you talk to me.

245
00:16:32,919 --> 00:16:33,720
If you don't ask me,

246
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:35,120
I won't save you.

247
00:16:36,320 --> 00:16:37,639
Even if you ask me,

248
00:16:37,960 --> 00:16:39,320
I won't save you.

249
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:41,440
After all, it's hard for me

250
00:16:41,480 --> 00:16:42,679
to dig the pit.

251
00:16:53,440 --> 00:16:54,559
Are you dead?

252
00:17:00,039 --> 00:17:01,000
Boring trick.

253
00:17:02,639 --> 00:17:03,200
Where's your brother?

254
00:17:03,919 --> 00:17:05,240
I advise you to stay away from my brother.

255
00:17:05,720 --> 00:17:06,799
He doesn't have the mood to deal with you.

256
00:17:10,279 --> 00:17:11,400
Look at you.

257
00:17:11,960 --> 00:17:13,680
I don't know if you ran away from home

258
00:17:13,799 --> 00:17:15,240
or were kicked out.

259
00:17:15,920 --> 00:17:16,480
Anyway,

260
00:17:16,680 --> 00:17:18,000
you were abandoned by your brother, right?

261
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:23,680
If you really have nowhere to go,

262
00:17:23,960 --> 00:17:24,920
I'll allow you to

263
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:26,279
be a bodyguard in my house.

264
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:27,880
I'll provide you with food and accommodation.

265
00:17:28,559 --> 00:17:29,880
Your family can come to see you.

266
00:17:30,079 --> 00:17:30,640
How about that?

267
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:31,519
Not bad, huh?

268
00:17:31,880 --> 00:17:32,559
You're so noisy.

269
00:17:33,200 --> 00:17:34,039
I'm not.

270
00:17:34,240 --> 00:17:36,160
Qin Yeren heard your plan at home.

271
00:17:44,920 --> 00:17:45,759
Surprised?

272
00:17:46,119 --> 00:17:48,079
I've got plenty of traps.

273
00:17:50,839 --> 00:17:52,279
Let go. You're hurting me.

274
00:17:53,119 --> 00:17:53,880
Hurry up.

275
00:17:55,799 --> 00:17:56,359
Don't

276
00:17:56,960 --> 00:17:58,359
mess with my brother.

277
00:17:59,039 --> 00:18:00,400
Do you want to see that woman

278
00:18:00,480 --> 00:18:01,359
by your brother's side?

279
00:18:02,279 --> 00:18:03,160
She can forget it.

280
00:18:03,519 --> 00:18:04,039
And you,

281
00:18:04,480 --> 00:18:05,160
forget it.

282
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:09,039
It's too early to say that.

283
00:18:10,119 --> 00:18:12,160
I will become Mrs. Lu sooner or later.

284
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:18,119
You have the same goal as me.

285
00:18:18,440 --> 00:18:19,519
Why don't we cooperate?
